property.caption: Filter Entity
property.description: Select the (none persistant) entity that can hold the current page name.

property.caption: Filter Page name
property.description: The attribute of the filter that will contain the current page name.

property.caption: Entity
property.description: Select the entity that has reminder notes in it.

property.caption: Reminder title
property.description: The attribute of the object to get / set the title off the reminder note.

property.caption: Reminder description
property.description: The attribute of the object to get / set the description off the reminder note.

property.caption: Reminder date
property.description: The attribute of the object to set the creation date of the reminder note.

property.caption: Reminder page
property.description: The attribute to save the page name where the reminder note is visible.

property.caption: Reminder X
property.description: The attribute to save the X position name where the reminder note is visible.

property.caption: Reminder Y
property.description: The attribute to save the Y position name where the reminder note is visible.

property.caption: Current user
property.description: The association to the current user.

property.caption: Get reminder notes.
property.description: The microflow to get all the reminder notes.

property.caption: Item click microflow
property.description: The microflow to execute when the item is clicked.

property.caption: Item delete microflow
property.description: The microflow to delete the note who is active.

property.caption: Entity user
property.description: Select the entity that is used for the user account.

property.caption: Entity fullname
property.description: The attribute from the user to readout the fullname.

property.caption: Get user.
property.description: The microflow to get the user.
